---
import TerminalSimulator from '../react/TerminalSimulator';
import SmartDownloader from '../react/SmartDownloader';
---

<section class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center mb-24">
  <div class="lg:col-span-6 space-y-6">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-brand-blue/10 border border-brand-blue/30 rounded-full text-brand-blue dark:text-brand-accent text-xs font-mono">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-brand-blue dark:bg-brand-accent rounded-full animate-pulse" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span data-i18n="hero_badge">本地沙箱隔离 · 基于 DeepSeek 大模型驱动</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-sans">
      <span data-i18n="hero_title_line1">拒绝黑盒，</span><br />
      掌控真正的 <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-blue to-blue-500 dark:from-brand-accent dark:to-brand-blue" data-i18n="hero_title_line2">AI 编程智能体</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-xl" data-i18n="hero_description">
      DeepFlow 是为极客量身定制的桌面端 AI 协同平台。通过原生 Electron 驱动本地工具（Bash/LSP/Git），构建双路径 ReAct 自闭环智能体，彻底告别只说不写的"被动型"AI。
    </p>

    <div id="download">
      <SmartDownloader client:visible />
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-brand-border/60">
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold font-mono text-brand-blue dark:text-brand-accent" data-i18n="hero_stat_tools">22 个</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400" data-i18n="hero_stat_tools_sub">内置高危/只读工具链</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold font-mono text-brand-blue dark:text-brand-accent" data-i18n="hero_stat_loop">Dual-Loop</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400" data-i18n="hero_stat_loop_sub">聊天流与独立 Agent 循环</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold font-mono text-brand-blue dark:text-brand-accent" data-i18n="hero_stat_local">100%</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400" data-i18n="hero_stat_local_sub">本地工作区/记忆沙箱化</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="react-demo" class="lg:col-span-6 relative">
    <TerminalSimulator client:visible />
  </div>
</section>
